trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en mängd <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListCollection class represents the aggregation of all the items in a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerActionListCollection representerar sammanställning av alla objekt i en panel med smarta etiketter.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListCollection class contains zero or more <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerActionListCollection innehåller noll eller fler <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekt.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: Each of these lists contains zero or more objects that represent the actual items in the panel and are derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> class.
trans-unit.target: Var och en av dessa listor innehåller noll eller flera objekt som representerar de faktiska artiklarna i panelen och härleds från <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem>klassen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem>

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the two techniques for supplying a DesignerActionListCollection to populate the panel with items for components, including custom controls.
trans-unit.target: I följande tabell visas de två metoder för att tillhandahålla en DesignerActionListCollection för att fylla i panelen med objekt för komponenter, inklusive anpassade kontroller.

trans-unit.source: |Technique|Description| |---------------|-----------------| |Pull model|The designer for the component class, which is derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> class, supplies this collection through the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: | Metoden | Beskrivning | |---------------|-----------------| | Pull-modellen | Designer för komponentklassen som har härletts från den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>klassen, tillhandahåller den här samlingen via den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The designer infrastructure reads this property when it must display the panel.| |Push model|A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> or DesignerActionListCollection is supplied as a parameter in a call to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> associated with the component.| The designer infrastructure constructs a panel by creating a smart tag panel, whose constructor takes two parameters of type DesignerActionListCollection.
trans-unit.target: Designer infrastrukturen läser den här egenskapen när den måste visa panelen. | | Push-modell | En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>eller DesignerActionListCollection anges som en parameter i ett anrop till <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A>metod för <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService>som är associerade med komponenten. | Designer infrastruktur skapas en panel genom att skapa en panel med smarta etiketter, vars konstruktorn har två parametrar av typen DesignerActionListCollection.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: The collections of lists, which contain the pulled and pushed items, are merged into one panel.
trans-unit.target: Samlingar med listor, som innehåller objekten ägardatabasen och intryckt slås samman i en panel.

trans-unit.source: Because it derives from the <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase?displayProperty=fullName> class, DesignerActionListCollection uses an internal <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> to store its collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom den härleds från den <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase?displayProperty=fullName>klass, DesignerActionListCollection använder en intern <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>för insamling av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekt.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> </xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the current collection into the supplied array, starting at the specified array index.
trans-unit.target: Kopierar elementen i den aktuella samlingen till den angivna matrisen som startar vid index för den angivna matrisen.

trans-unit.source: If the CopyTo method throws an exception while copying, the state of the destination array is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Om metoden CopyTo genererar ett undantag vid kopiering, är tillståndet för Målmatrisen odefinierad.

trans-unit.source: For example, if an <xref:System.ArgumentException> or <xref:System.InvalidCastException> occurs, the destination array may be left in a partially filled state.
